Package: eemr
Type: Package
Title: Coherence-Based Expression Module (EEM) Search
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Atsushi", "Niida", email = "atusiniida@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R bindings (via Rcpp) for the eemCpp coherence-based expression
    module search tool. Given an expression matrix and a collection of
    candidate gene sets, eem_search() finds coherently expressed subsets of
    each gene set ("expression modules") and assigns them a significance
    p-value based on a permutation test.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/atusiniida/eemr, https://atusiniida.github.io/eemr/
BugReports: https://github.com/atusiniida/eemr/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports: Rcpp
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
